name: Pixel Run V1.1.1
body:
# Pixel Runner V1.1.1
controls: A: kick
          W: jump
          S: slide
          D: launch

## new updates: 
4/17/2014---fixed minor gravity bug, altered point system to accept gold bar bonuses

### Description:

       Pixel Runner is a simple yet addicting game
 made by up-and coming programmer Kbossthegreat.
It uses JavaScript coding to provide a smooth gameplay, 
and dynamic controls aid performance. 
Try to get a great point value before you die, 
then respawn and try again!

## Suggestions or Questions? Bug reports?
contact at: kbossthegreat@outlook.com
